        </p>

        <h2>8. Data Processing</h2>
        <p>
          Our processing of personal data is governed by our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>. By using the Service, you acknowledge that:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email content is processed in transit and <strong>is not stored</strong></li>
